title: Congratulations to MAgIC lab undergraduate student Guanqi He on his graduation!
description: Guanqi He joined the MAgIC lab in 2021 and conducted research in output regulation under the supervision of Prof. Yang Wang. He graduated in June 2023 with the title of Outstanding Undergraduate Student of University of ShanghaiTech. Guanqi will go to Carnegie Mellon University to continue his research on control and robotics.
